{"id":"da6f1442-ef20-4318-9296-4e09437f0e81","title":"1556/10/31: To Lionardo di Buonarroto Simoni, dearest nephew","type":"main-list-block","children":[{"id":"57ef6025-ec06-4e21-a753-a798b5fd3477","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"From Rome, October 31st, 1556.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"8e7985bc-cdfa-4481-9320-1f205e600e88","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":0,"end":3,"value":"8532f2fa-b614-4eed-9eae-586327f6a15a","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"9ede24ba-f9cd-4560-9f45-ef1e8ef3d72f","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":5,"end":8,"value":"501a8a32-2c8a-4934-9060-8c7e36339f0f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"627b9869-eb50-4c30-8839-fcb7ecd32394","type":"codex/time-reference","start":11,"end":28,"value":"4bedab99-71dc-46e8-a7e6-9ccf0641c906","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"00797f25-36d0-4912-8126-f3112c9973e4","type":"style/superscript","start":21,"end":22,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"71c1263c-ea2f-4845-874b-7533a4ceebf5","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"To Lionardo di Buonarroto Simoni, dearest nephew,","standoffProperties":[{"id":"6caa6f75-1984-4fad-8103-640001e6cd14","type":"style/italics","start":0,"end":47,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"0a0780f4-5a52-4f92-8071-86f52a7787fe","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":3,"end":31,"value":"93ce2119-f2b8-4642-b551-7b8ca6b1ed96","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"52ba0997-fe6d-4550-9dc7-47beca017e3b","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"in Florence.\u00A0Sent to the Cortesi, who are asked","standoffProperties":[{"id":"5e1862f1-3750-425b-9c46-ce6291dc2dea","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":3,"end":10,"value":"671ee7e7-ae1b-4a5a-9591-b40203d5108f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"5c5876dd-7dd4-410a-9956-61a6c833c322","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":25,"end":31,"value":"55123dc2-da4c-46ba-9829-590987bfb40f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"73373a8e-46fd-458d-a30e-9a639fc3aa4f","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":34,"end":36,"value":"55123dc2-da4c-46ba-9829-590987bfb40f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"5cb787a7-3d57-40e5-9f9a-ae441990b256","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"to give it immediately into his hands. In","standoffProperties":[{"id":"010d7bcf-a2b1-4e41-94ef-9a30074d6dac","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":28,"end":30,"value":"93ce2119-f2b8-4642-b551-7b8ca6b1ed96","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"7572a770-4821-4380-bafd-720c62a8a7ef","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":39,"end":40,"value":"0c663cc2-dd9f-40ce-b17b-734e41b369ef","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"e20e5466-3989-42b9-ae73-add5f2741999","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"Florence.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"dd5387a0-4573-474d-8aa9-a767e5f035bd","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":0,"end":7,"value":"671ee7e7-ae1b-4a5a-9591-b40203d5108f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"07dda50c-59e2-4b85-8a03-1adf299c75a2","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"","standoffProperties":[],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"a9372e25-5a2d-444a-ad22-49c2ec256503","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"Lionardo, dearest nephew,\u00A0\u2014\u00A0A few days ago I received a letter from thee to which I did not reply\u00A0earlier as I had no opportunity for doing so. But now I will make up for it, not because I wish to astonish thee but so that thou mayst understand what has been happening. More than a month ago, finding\u00A0that the work upon the fabric of St. Peter\u0027s had begun to slow down, I made up my mind to go to Loreto as an act of devotion; but when I got as far as Spoleto\u00A0I found myself rather fatigued and accordingly remained there a little while to rest. The consequence was that I was prevented from carrying out my intention, for a man had been sent off post-haste to tell me I was to go back to Rome. In order not to disobey I therefore turned back towards Rome, where by the grace of God I now am. The condition\u00A0of affairs with respect to these present perils is in God\u0027s\u00A0hands, so that I need say no more, save that there is\u00A0a good prospect of peace being established. Please God it may be so. Take care of thy health and pray God to help us.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"f63d8fc7-850a-470b-969e-17185c51ec83","type":"style/uppercase","start":0,"end":23,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"70960309-4f1c-4804-bf02-b16839539ba3","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":0,"end":7,"value":"93ce2119-f2b8-4642-b551-7b8ca6b1ed96","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"03e2742f-c4cc-4b58-b792-b7c1742cf5b3","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":18,"end":23,"value":"93ce2119-f2b8-4642-b551-7b8ca6b1ed96","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"af6eeb3c-d0ec-4456-b727-c6ea2491e918","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":43,"end":43,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"373b71d2-88d7-41b7-90ef-8291c8a46bcc","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":68,"end":71,"value":"93ce2119-f2b8-4642-b551-7b8ca6b1ed96","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"1d087f3c-89e8-4ebc-9080-3b001597e442","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":82,"end":82,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"41f434fb-9b43-453e-a1f5-93591e485d77","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":109,"end":109,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"2f8bac7b-9d54-4984-bb5b-9df9a578dd81","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":152,"end":152,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"125494c9-0da9-485b-a41c-29e166196f1f","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":187,"end":187,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"d5b86bcf-d675-4017-b4ea-6b54f3c64dec","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":206,"en